\title{Capability Security Stack}
\author{bmorphism}
\date{2026-04-03}
\taxon{index}

\p{Object capability security from theory to implementation. The BCI decode
stage (Stage 4) outputs capability-secured neural intent via OCapN. The
stack runs: Spritely Goblins → OCapN → CapTP → wire format (Cap'n Proto /
Syrup). GF(3) conservation ensures no capability is created or destroyed
— only transferred.}

